00:41:39,830 --> 00:41:41,070
<i>Bravo.</i>

966
00:41:42,132 --> 00:41:45,443
<i>Oh, wow! Harper, that was wonderful!</i>

967
00:41:45,636 --> 00:41:46,614
<i>I stunk.</i>

968
00:41:46,804 --> 00:41:47,805
<i>You most certainly did not!</i>

969
00:41:49,707 --> 00:41:51,414
<i>Wasn't she wonderful?</i>

970
00:41:51,609 --> 00:41:52,417
<i>No.</i>

971
00:41:52,610 --> 00:41:54,783
<i>This will not be good enough
