980
00:42:17,368 --> 00:42:19,609
<i>I got this audition
to be the local weather girl.</i>

981
00:42:19,803 --> 00:42:21,714
<i>Well, I was so uptight.</i>

982
00:42:21,906 --> 00:42:25,183
<i>Artie took me out the night before and we
