983
00:42:25,376 --> 00:42:27,447
<i>And the next day I got the job.</i>

984
00:42:28,145 --> 00:42:29,681
<i>So, you're saying I should drink?</i>

985
00:42:30,948 --> 00:42:32,689
<i>No, no, no. I'm not saying that.</i>

986
00:42:32,883 --> 00:42:35,523
<i>I am saying that perhaps you could relax.</i>

987
00:42:35,719 --> 00:42:36,993
<i>You could go out with your friends.</i>

988
00:42:37,187 --> 00:42:40,031
<i>You could have some fun Friday night.
