00:42:54,204 --> 00:42:56,844
<i>I have to practice every second!</i>

995
00:43:00,411 --> 00:43:01,788
<i>Doctor Schveer?</i>

996
00:43:02,313 --> 00:43:03,383
<i>Yes?</i>

997
00:43:03,581 --> 00:43:05,356
<i>Perhaps we got off on the wrong foot.</i>

998
00:43:05,549 --> 00:43:06,721
<i>But I would like to let you know that...</i>

999
00:43:06,917 --> 00:43:09,557
<i>if you ever speak
