1001
00:43:11,155 --> 00:43:12,429
<i>but some red hair and an accent!</i>

1002
00:43:12,623 --> 00:43:14,398
<i>Is that clear, comrade?</i>

1003
00:43:38,816 --> 00:43:40,625
<i>Ooh! Thank you. Here you go.</i>

1004
00:43:40,884 --> 00:43:42,022
<i>Mmm!</i>

1005
00:43:44,488 --> 00:43:45,489
<i>Carcinogens.</i>

1006
00:43:46,523 --> 00:43:47,831
<i>Oh, the first one just laid a base.</i>

1007
00:43:48,025 --> 00:43:50,505
<i>This is the real thing. I'm at the ballpark.</i>

1008
00:43:54,765 --> 00:43:56,403
<i>He likes baseball, huh?</i>

1009
00:43:56,600 --> 00:43:57,578
<i>Yeah, he likes lots of things.</i>

1010
00:43:57,768 --> 00:44:01,272
<i>He likes sports.
