1011
00:44:01,472 --> 00:44:02,780
<i>He likes cake.</i>

1012
00:44:02,973 --> 00:44:04,145
<i>Touché.</i>

1013
00:44:05,009 --> 00:44:07,853
<i>He's just hidden behind that... stutter.</i>

1014
00:44:08,045 --> 00:44:10,651
<i>Well, you know, kids have a way
