00:44:11,148 --> 00:44:12,126
<i>No, they don't, Dad.</i>

1016
00:44:12,316 --> 00:44:13,989
<i>That's why there's prison.</i>

1017
00:44:16,487 --> 00:44:17,488
<i>All right, guys, bring it in!</i>

1018
00:44:17,688 --> 00:44:19,258
<i>Bring it in! Get all those hands in there.</i>

1019
00:44:19,456 --> 00:44:20,366
<i>Come on.</i>

1020
00:44:20,557 --> 00:44:23,834
<i>Everybody on three. One, two, three...</i>

1021
00:44:24,028 --> 00:44:25,974
<i>Let's have fun!</i>

1022
00:44:27,231 --> 00:44:29,711
<i>I am so excited about this.</i>

1023
00:44:30,234 --> 00:44:31,178
<i>Let's play!</i>

1024
00:44:31,368 --> 00:44:32,278
<i>He's pitching!</i>

1025
00:44:32,469 --> 00:44:33,209
<i>Yeah.</i>

1026
00:44:33,404 --> 00:44:34,405
<i>He has a good arm.</i>

1027
00:44:34,505 --> 00:44:35,483
<i>Like Mom, like son.</i>

1028
00:44:35,673 --> 00:44:36,651
<i>Yeah, right.</i>

1029
00:44:36,840 --> 00:44:38,183
<i>No, you had a hose.</i>

1030
00:44:38,375 --> 00:44:40,116
<i>But then you hit puberty
and you got all girlie on me.</i>

1031
00:44:40,310 --> 00:44:42,312
<i>Well, gee, Dad,
I'm so sorry that I hit puberty.</i>

1032
00:44:42,513 --> 00:44:43,651
<i>I was so proud of you back then.</i>

1033
00:44:43,847 --> 00:44:45,520
<i>You were usually the only girl out there.</i>

1034
00:44:45,916 --> 00:44:48,123
<i>You used to stand up to those stinky boys.</i>

1035
00:44:48,318 --> 00:44:50,229
<i>Do you remember that summer
when you worked for me in the booth...</i>

1036
00:44:50,421 --> 00:44:52,162
<i>keeping score and doing stats?</i>

1037
00:44:52,356 --> 00:44:53,733
<i>You were so cute, sitting there</i>

1038
00:44:53,824 --> 00:44:55,861
<i>- scrunched over your little pencil.</i>

1039
00:44:56,360 --> 00:44:57,862
<i>You never saw that ball coming, did you?</i>

1040
00:44:58,062 --> 00:44:59,166
<i>You could have yelled "Incoming</i>

1041
00:44:59,363 --> 00:45:01,206
<i>I was on the air.
