1042
00:45:01,398 --> 00:45:03,173
<i>You do love that job.</i>

1043
00:45:03,367 --> 00:45:04,402
<i>- Yeah.
- Yeah.</i>

1044
00:45:04,601 --> 00:45:05,579
<i>Yeah, I do.</i>

1045
00:45:05,769 --> 00:45:06,747
<i>Batter up!</i>

1046
00:45:08,072 --> 00:45:09,551
<i>Ah! This is that bully kid.</i>

1047
00:45:09,740 --> 00:45:10,912
<i>Yeah, Ivan.</i>

1048
00:45:11,108 --> 00:45:13,486
<i>I would so like to see Turner strike him out.</i>

1049
00:45:23,887 --> 00:45:24,524
<i>Strike!</i>

1050
00:45:24,955 --> 00:45:28,198
<i>Strike one!
Hey, he is really good. He's really good.</i>

1051
00:45:28,392 --> 00:45:29,871
<i>Way to go, Turner!</i>

1052
00:45:30,060 --> 00:45:31,038
<i>Turner Simmons on the mound...</i>

1053
00:45:31,228 --> 00:45:33,708
<i>a young Cuban prospect
who escaped on a raft.</i>

1054
00:45:33,897 --> 00:45:35,342
<i>He's facing Ivan, a miserable child</i>

1055
00:45:35,432 --> 00:45:36,843
<i>who is loathed and despised by everyone.</i>

1056
00:45:37,034 --> 00:45:38,069
<i>- Dad!</i>

1057
00:45:41,238 --> 00:45:43,878
<i>Swing and a miss! Strike two! Hoo-hoo!</i>

1058
00:45:43,974 --> 00:45:45,578
<i>One more strike and it's back</i>

1059
00:45:45,676 --> 00:45:47,212
<i>to the dugout
for this eight-year-old bullfrog.</i>

1060
00:45:47,411 --> 00:45:48,321
<i>Dad...</i>

1061
00:45:48,545 --> 00:45:51,651
<i>The yearbook said
Ivan is "Most likely to do time."</i>

1062
00:45:53,684 --> 00:45:55,027
<i>Simmons looks at him.</i>

1063
00:45:57,287 --> 00:45:58,322
<i>He shakes it off.</i>

1064
00:46:02,593 --> 00:46:03,571
<i>Here's the pitch.</i>

1065
00:46:04,695 --> 00:46:07,232
<i>Strike three!
