1066
00:46:08,932 --> 00:46:10,502
<i>Lights out, Alice!</i>

1067
00:46:13,971 --> 00:46:15,917
<i>Way to go, Turner! Way to look!</i>

1068
00:46:16,173 --> 00:46:18,619
<i>Oh, whoa, whoa, whoa.
