1069
00:46:18,942 --> 00:46:20,922
<i>One, two, three! Out of there!</i>

1070
00:46:21,145 --> 00:46:22,419
<i>Time!</i>

1071
00:46:22,880 --> 00:46:23,915
<i>It's okay!</i>

1072
00:46:24,114 --> 00:46:26,185
<i>This is my dad and he's new here!</i>

1073
00:46:26,483 --> 00:46:29,123
<i>Oh, okay. There are no outs in this game.</i>

1074
00:46:29,787 --> 00:46:31,630
<i>No outs? How is that possible?</i>

1075
00:46:31,822 --> 00:46:35,360
<i>They hit until they get on base.</i>

1076
00:46:35,559 --> 00:46:37,266
<i>- Seriously?
- Seriously.</i>

1077
00:46:37,461 --> 00:46:39,099
<i>- Dad, why don't we just sit down?
- Oh...</i>

1078
00:46:41,064 --> 00:46:42,042
<i>All right.</i>

1079
00:46:42,800 --> 00:46:44,108
<i>But you know that's kind of stupid!</i>

1080
00:46:44,301 --> 00:46:46,747
<i>Because if you just think of the song...</i>

1081
00:46:46,937 --> 00:46:49,213
<i>'Cause it's one, two,
three strikes, you're out...</i>

1082
00:46:49,406 --> 00:46:50,749
<i>at the old ball game</i>

1083
00:46:50,941 --> 00:46:51,646
<i>Not...</i>

1084
00:46:51,842 --> 00:46:53,219
<i>until you get a hit</i>

1085
00:46:53,410 --> 00:46:55,890
<i>He's right!
