1086
00:46:56,079 --> 00:46:58,650
<i>The point is for the kids
to enjoy the game without competition.</i>

1087
00:46:58,849 --> 00:47:00,226
<i>Yeah, but competition is the game.</i>

1088
00:47:00,417 --> 00:47:01,487
<i>You know, it's like life.</i>

1089
00:47:01,685 --> 00:47:02,789
<i>Let me ask you something.</i>

1090
00:47:02,986 --> 00:47:04,431
<i>I mean, how do you even
