1091
00:47:04,755 --> 00:47:06,234
<i>In this league, we don't keep score.</i>

1092
00:47:06,790 --> 00:47:09,794
<i>Every game ends in a tie.</i>

1093
00:47:10,961 --> 00:47:12,235
<i>Oh, no.</i>

1094
00:47:12,429 --> 00:47:15,501
<i>No agony of defeat? Just the thrill of a tie?</i>

1095
00:47:15,699 --> 00:47:17,269
<i>It's good they don't keep score!</i>

1096
00:47:17,467 --> 00:47:18,775
<i>Yeah, 'cause your kid stinks.</i>

1097
00:47:18,969 --> 00:47:20,505
<i>Oh, I will bust you up!</i>

1098
00:47:20,704 --> 00:47:22,274
<i>The old guy's right. It's boring.</i>

1099
00:47:22,472 --> 00:47:23,109
<i>See?</i>

1100
00:47:23,307 --> 00:47:25,048
<i>It is not boring!</i>

1101
00:47:25,409 --> 00:47:27,218
<i>They're children and they're having fun!</i>

1102
00:47:27,411 --> 00:47:29,755
